headline: TRV Q4 Deep Dive: AI Investments and Underwriting Discipline Shape Outlook for 2026
summary: Property and casualty insurer Travelers (NYSE:TRV) announced better-than-expected revenue in Q4 CY2025, with sales up 3.2% year on year to $12.45 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $11.13 per share was 26.8% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
